动过（机器）。”刘女士提出，当初安装时系统应该会留下安装记录和留存照片，可以比照看看，对方则告诉她记录只留存三年，现在看不了了。净水器两根水管确实装反“好水被排掉的话，那么喝的就是废水。”“直饮水可以直接饮用，而‘废水’比自来水还要脏。”小米净水器水管接反，女子称喝5年“废水”，安装师傅：比自来水还脏"},"attached_info":"CkIImdbi17vt2sQ/EAMaCTExNDA4Mzk4MSCajvC+BjAAOPEFQBVyCzE1NDM1MjM5MjcxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"59 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-d3cf7601b44ccaee03aeff4239f99b92_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1742560097.123279","card_id":"Q_651185892","target":{"id":651185892,"title":"中国传统武术到底能不能实战？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/651185892","type":"question","created":1711959266,"answer_count":460,"follower_count":689,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[5749,65530],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAImdbi17vt2sQ/EAMaCTEwNjk4NTgwNCDi2amwBjAAOLEFQBZyCTY1MTE4NTg5MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"58 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-de4c18107accaa467d6a9362da9724a6_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1742560097.123486","card_id":"Q_578172542","target":{"id":578172542,"title":"Linux 下常用的程序调试器 gdb 是什么原理？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/578172542","type":"question","created":1673463547,"answer_count":16,"follower_count":217,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1355,43335,88287],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8Imdbi17vt2sQ/EAMaCDkwNzY0MzYzIPuN/J0GMAA42QFAF3IJNTc4MTcyNTQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"58 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-b88b302d1b